Package: CalcRelAb
Title: Getting Relative Abundances From Phyloseq
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Imogen", "Porter", , "imogenp@student.ubc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9451-8606"))
Description: When provided a phyloseq object, transforms it into a dataframe using psmelt(). This is used to return an R dataframe of microbiome composition data containing sample ID and all other provided metadata, taxonomic information, abundance values, and relative abundance values. Abundance values of NA are dropped.
